  render_theorem(sec, "Lie Rank Sum Theorem (S237)", "Sum of ranks: (D^3-1) + (K^2-1) + (E^2-1) + (b^2-1) + (L-1) = 7 + 8 + 24 + 48 + 10 = 97 = G = bridge coupling. Three roads to G: Lie ranks, Hamming degree, mirror trace. All arrive at the same number.");
